{"tid":2248730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不斷出假topic 假政治post疲勞轟炸 港人正中共匪下懷","createTime":"2020-10-18T22:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T03:38:36.000Z","uid":4672,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d96ce8d0feb9fe5f0524462482eed243e5534a83","tid":2248730,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T22:53:34.000Z","msg":"呢類post有一個共通特點 <br />\n讓人感到 <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">強烈無力感 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n包括各種報導壞消息 中共又點點點侵犯香港<br />\n而港人無力反抗等等 <br />\n<br />\n呢類 「類新聞post」 不會提供任何解決方法<br />\n亦沒有任何安慰讀者言語 <br />\n<span class=\"orange\">單純地消磨港人意志和精神力 <br />\n用各種假標題吸引讀者 <br />\n將寶貴既注意力和時間就白白浪費係呢d冇價值post<br />\n佔據所有頭版 熱門位置<br />\n<br />\n目的只為令真正有價值既post無人訪問<br />\n並且通過不斷地疲勞轟炸去使香港人逐漸厭倦<br />\n </span><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係共產黨對付港人(連登)最新策略"},{"pid":"db971228718cefc4f6792f360fda65c66c646ebd","tid":2248730,"uid":68111,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T22:56:41.000Z","msg":"唔新架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14年用到而家"},{"pid":"74ab708a62898253ad725c3739c8f795bd24aca1","tid":2248730,"uid":4672,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"db971228718cefc4f6792f360fda65c66c646ebd","tid":2248730,"uid":68111,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T22:56:41.000Z","msg":"唔新架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14年用到而家"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:01:29.000Z","msg":"近呢兩個月cc台可以話已經進入「淪陷」情況<br />\n同一個「類新聞」post 幾百個人開<br />\n對抗中共侵略討論則沉到落太平洋馬里亞納海溝的最深處"},{"pid":"1728811daad70076c9d0074d3e247b047ae275a1","tid":2248730,"uid":13343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db971228718cefc4f6792f360fda65c66c646ebd","tid":2248730,"uid":68111,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T22:56:41.000Z","msg":"唔新架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14年用到而家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:05:57.000Z","msg":"近一年開始係大規模日日夜夜炸<br />\n<b